Stunning, exquisite, and on the most sought-after private lake in East Texas, this stately and captivating home will mesmerize you.  It offers absolutely every amenity imaginable. The master suite is a paradise featuring a remote controlled fireplace, spectacular view of the lake, deck with Jacuzzi, outside shower, a waterfall bath, heated floors, aromatherapy infused steam shower, coffee station, and much more. The kitchen is a chef's dream with a gas six-burner stove double oven, warming drawer, faucet with a hands-free operation (foot pedal). The large living space boasts spectacular views and a fireplace with massive solid piece marble hearth andmwood storage. Downstairs offers two large bedrooms, two full baths, large living space and kitchenette, a large saferoom, and a whole-house water purifier. The 3-level "garage-mahal"! This is a car collector's dream with every amenity you can think of! The lift from the lower level to the main center level, floor lighting, three air jets, 3 overhead doors, built-in tool cabinet with pneumatic drawer, washer and dryer, spiral staircase to the upstairs man cave. Outside, enjoy a lovely covered patio complete with a cooking station and large seating area. The 3 stall boathouse and a party bar and upper deck give you a birds' eye view of the annual Fourth of July fireworks. A few other amenities include lake fed sprinkler system, Generac whole house generator, robot mower for lakeside yard, a security system with remotes, a 6x6 lift in the main 2 car garage for Christmas tree, & MORE!
